\cf0 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Every single person in this room right now has been given an assignment!\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The problem is many of us don\'92t want it.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}There is a temptation in all of us to want to live someone else\'92s life.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}If I just had a wife or husband like them\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}If I had his job or their kids or better health or whatever.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}If I didn\'92t have all this debt I could give more\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}If God had gifted me differently\'85then I could be more effective!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We live vicariously through others in the form of celebrities\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0
\f4\b \cf5 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Don\'92t copy someone else\'92s life in \
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl1
\f3\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}How they raise their kids\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}How they spend their money\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}How they dress and act\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You have a calling and it is unique and for you only\'85embrace it and run with it not from it.\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl1
\f4\b \cf5 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Be Purple!\
